&lt;li&gt;Help manage organizational change related to AI implementation and workflow transformation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build resources, documentation, and SOPs related to AI usage and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the implementation and optimization of AI tools and platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track and report on AI initiative outcomes, adoption metrics, productivity improvements, and operational impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help ensure AI usage aligns with company policies, compliance requirements, and operational goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain organized documentation related to AI initiatives, workflows, and training materials.&lt;/li&gt;
